query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `taxonomia_imports` (
  `id` varchar(36) NOT NULL,
  `batch_id` varchar(36) NOT NULL UNIQUE,
  `total_disciplinas` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
  `total_assuntos` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
  `total_topicos` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
  `status` enum('ATIVO','DESFEITO') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'ATIVO',
  `imported_by` varchar(36) NOT NULL,
  `created_at` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `undone_at` timestamp NULL,
  `undone_by` varchar(36) NULL,
  CONSTRAINT `taxonomia_imports_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`),
  KEY `idx_batch_id` (`batch_id`),
  KEY `idx_status` (`status`),
  KEY `idx_created_at` (`created_at`)
);
